name: GRAPE APE STRAIN
description: GRAPE APE STRAIN by Iggy Nugget #NFTsForAll #WorldArtDay2021 Grape Ape is a tasty, memorable strain with strong indica roots. Its distinctive look and complex fruity flavor makes it an easy favorite -- to say nothing of its incredibly potent body high. Grape Ape is the product of strains as different as Mendocino Purps, an award-winning Northern California crossbreed, the influential staple strain Skunk, and a legendary Afghani landrace.
